<collectingCountry box="[589,659,392,418]" name="China" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">China</collectingCountry>
adults fly in August, up to 
<quantity box="[980,1069,392,418]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" unit="m" value="1200.0">1200 m</quantity>
on northwestern altiplano.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
